that not much wisdom is required to govern the world.

            As
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">recompense</ENAMEX>--small though it be--for the pleasure I have got from <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Bartlett</ENAMEX>, I am
